      "title": "Notification regarding power outage",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) has today approved the power cut schedule for Monday (15) and Tuesday (16) for 1 hour 20 minutes.",
        "Accordingly, A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I,J,K,L,P,Q,R,S,T,U, 1 hour and 20 minutes for sections V and W Power cut will be enforced from 5.00 pm to 9.00 pm for the divisions."
      ],
